		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I guess it would be possible to adress more ROM by using other pins, such as the CHR ROM upper adress, in order to get 1024 KB of PRG ROM split into two big chunks of 512 kb, but then CHRROM would be restricted to 128 KB, and this wouldn't be emulatable unless an emulator was written espeically for this.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


